The paper focuses on training deep convolutional neural networks for facial expression recognition, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses different approaches to utilizing multiple noisy labels, which is a common problem in machine learning and falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the creation of an enhanced data set, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
